view slideshow
---------------
example - "testimonial sidebar block" connect scrolling like slideshow

module name - view slideshow 
supporting file - jquery.cycle.all.js

steps
-----
1. download "view slideshow" module and enable it
2. download "jquery.cycle.all.js" file
3. create folder "jquery.cycle" in "/sites/all/libraries/"
4. paste "jquery.cycle.all.js" file in "/sites/all/libraries/jquery.cycle" folder
5. create "block View" based on Testimonial content types.
6. select "Format" option in block view configuration setting
  - set to "view slideshow" option
	- set other slideshow time and style option
7. save and enjoy
